name: Friendship bracelets - Yellow - Set of 4 bracelets
description:
Friendship bracelets designed by fashion blogger Taisa Veras in collaboration with jewelry designer Adriana Unarreal. 

Product Info:

- One Size fits all (they're expandable).
-They come in sets of 4 single bracelets that can be worn together or separate.
-Charms are one-of-a-kind.
-Each bracelet is hand-made.
